```latex
\documentclass[12pt]{article} % or book, report, etc., depending on your document type

\begin{document}

% Generate the Table of Contents (ToC)
\tableofcontents

\section{Introduction}
This is the introduction section. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. 

